{"tid":1615213,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[行動post] 終極大整合，裝修全攻略","createTime":"2019-10-03T04:28:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T08:37:31.000Z","uid":192824,"like":34,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"58493ca276e6ffbe5434305f0acdece4df3d444a","tid":1615213,"uid":192824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T04:28:46.000Z","msg":"由禽晚快閃行動開始，連登出現好多警世Post，有D都有可取之處。見仲未有人出本裝修說明書，咁我就出本先，歡迎大家再用我POST加以整合。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">整合日期: 2019年10月3日中午12時</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">0. 引言</span></span></strong></ins><br />\n<br />\n<strong>割蓆宣言<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1614174\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1614174</a></strong><br />\n<br />\n鑑於警暴日趨嚴重，而且有部分店舖助紂為虐，市民給於該些商舖或建築適當懲處，而只會懲處該部分商店或建築，但該店或建築任何錢財最終只會出現於該店。<br />\n<br />\n如若有人趁機假扮示威者，或以香復香港名義於其他商店或建築內以個人私心為目的，偷竊任何錢財、無差別破壞以達至獲得任何形式的個人利益，階與示威者無關。<br />\n---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<strong>［唔止民意撚］唔好變成真正暴徒<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1614686\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1614686</a></strong><br />\n<br />\n行動一定要有原則。所以我倡議：<br />\n1. 對家反對=罷買<br />\n2. 對家對手足動私刑，或直接支援極權對手足行刑=拆佢老母<br />\n3. 我地不姦淫擄掠，不傷及平民<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 鎖定目標</span></span></strong></ins><br />\n<br />\n<strong>破壞商舖請合乎比例原則<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1613194\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1613194</a></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">【建議行為準則】</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n行為：美心集團發表撐警、奶共言論<br />\n目的：懲罰美心集團<br />\n手段：罷買、紙鏈可以達到「目的」，同時「合乎比例」<br />\n<br />\n行為：福建幫／黑社會斬人<br />\n目的：懲罰福建幫／黑社會商舖：例如二陂坊麻雀館<br />\n手段：裝修商舖可以達到「目的」，同時「合乎比例」<br />\n<br />\n行為：Indigo hotel 篤灰<br />\n目的：懲罰Indigo hotel 篤灰<br />\n手段：裝修酒店可以達到「目的」，同時「合乎比例」<br />\n<br />\n行為：黨鐵容許721, 831無差別襲擊，任意停鐵路<br />\n目的：懲罰黨鐵<br />\n手段：裝修黨鐵可以達到「目的」，同時「合乎比例」<br />\n---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<strong>紅背景裝修、藍店罷買、黃店懲罰<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1615026\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1615026</a></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">紅</span></span>裝修<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">藍</span></span>罷買<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">黃</span></span></strong>懲罰</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2. 裝修過程</span></span></strong></ins><br />\n<br />\n<strong>[重要] 爆舖三大條款<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1614848\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1614848</a></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">1&gt; 必須要在當眼地方留下宣言/標語</span></span><br />\n例子:<br />\n福建幫打香港人<br />\n美心害港, 不了<br />\n殺人黨鐵<br />\n天滅中共<br />\n等等等<br />\n<br />\n十分重要! 因為好多港豬真係唔明點解我地要爆舖!<br />\n必定要留低字解釋宣傳<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">2&gt; 不可放火!不可放火!不可放火!不可放火!</span></span><br />\n唔同空擴地方, 密閉地方切記不可用火<br />\n火好難控制, 如果一唔小心好可能出大事<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">3&gt; 只傷舖, 不傷人</span></span><br />\n店員都係打份工, <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔出手唔篤灰</span></span>既話千萬唔可以傷人<br />\n---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<strong>前線手足求你入嚟花3秒睇睇，可以改變全場革命<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1614758\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1614758</a></strong><br />\n<br />\n例如中銀就「<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">BoCPC</span></strong></span>」(Bank of CPC)，黨鐵噴「黨鐵」連下面個logo (<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">一横一勾鐮刀，一舊一棟斧頭</span></span></strong>)，優品噴「<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">Fukien 360</span></span></strong>」，諗唔到嘅就加個prefix「Chi-」，例如「ChiMaxim」「ChiYoshinoya」等等<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">3. 裝修完成</span></span></strong></ins><br />\n<br />\n<strong>俾時間中共壟斷民生經濟就太遲，18區清算行動應馬上開始<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1612009\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1612009</a></strong><br />\n<br />\n手足裝修完記得簽 <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">#Anti-Chinazi</span></span></strong><br />\n文宣「針對性打擊」<br />\n不是「無差別破壞」<br />\n---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<strong>[文宣]裝修手足麻煩完事後痴依啲文宣係鋪頭<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1615023\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1615023</a></strong><br />\n<br />\n文宣圖入link 攞。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">第一次出整合Post，歡迎大家拎去加以修改。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>祝各位武運亨昌</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"3a58f83d07dc97b7d30fde40a0345abcec443a30","tid":1615213,"uid":56305,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T04:29:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9qWjEjz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9qWjEjz.jpg&h=418a9d94&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3a6036df717ef07061b690a20944f745480c7e19","tid":1615213,"uid":192824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T04:30:22.000Z","msg":"自推<br />\n1/10 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7ff7dc672e370ed597327161654e9e25c6274e3","tid":1615213,"uid":192824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T04:30:34.000Z","msg":"自推<br />\n2/10 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d822d85389bd36f08e773e6c065775f8405eeb8","tid":1615213,"uid":192824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T04:30:46.000Z","msg":"自推<br />\n3/10 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f8573a8f8f4fbe96be207a1a24c60d0c1232a22","tid":1615213,"uid":192824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T04:30:59.000Z","msg":"自推<br />\n4/10 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a71903d5cf7b5d3420c442e84e3d09a3df39b0cc","tid":1615213,"uid":192824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T04:31:11.000Z","msg":"自推<br />\n5/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08b584de96d3e3f70999cc9c06ada91f785e2cff","tid":1615213,"uid":192824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T04:31:24.000Z","msg":"自推<br />\n6/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eb62fbbdb2973e111179c7e5153c02425c42db3","tid":1615213,"uid":192824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T04:31:35.000Z","msg":"自推<br />\n7/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e3e055f26a6404e4cea596b571a2b4de822cb2d","tid":1615213,"uid":192824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T04:31:47.000Z","msg":"自推<br />\n8/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b19b59e9a283cba6e09c5e299995dd1e6ab6681b","tid":1615213,"uid":137143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T04:31:54.000Z","msg":"幫你推下"},{"pid":"85b2384f619371184481f166b65b27d576d21340","tid":1615213,"uid":192824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c